atomic design is deviding the componenets into atoms , moliciols , orgnism , templeates and pages 

atoms are the only componenets that can exsist on its own

system design in general is the creation of all atoms , thier guidelines , best practices and how to merge them togeather to create a moliciols

your role as an engineer 
    you need to transliate the guildlines into reusable code that can be used to create products in the future